title: A Tuna Christmas (1996) DVD-RIP 720.mp4
description:
A Tuna Christmas


Written by Jaston Williams, Joe Sears, and Ed Howard


Directed by Ed Howard


Starring TonyÂ® Award-Nominated Original Broadway Cast: Joe Sears and Jaston Williams


From the DVD cover:


Seasons Greetings from A TUNA CHRISTMAS, the Broadway smash hit and hilarious sequel to the hit comedy, GREATER TUNA, starring Tony Award-nominated Joe Sears and Jaston Williams. Nationally acclaimed and loved by audiences and critics alike, master comedians Sears and Williams, with their deft comic timing, trademark characterizations, and split-second costume changes, return to portray all 24 polyester-clad citizens of Tuna, the third smallest town in Texas, where the Lion's Club is too liberal and Patsy Cline never dies! This time, it's 24 hours before Christmas and the delightfully eccentric characters are attempting to cope with seasonal traumas such as a disaster-prone little theatre production of A CHRISTMAS CAROL and a yard decorating contest being sabotaged by a mysterious Christmas phantom
